of the Free Navy.

564
00:51:00.516 --> 00:51:03.226
and that Laconia
is yours and your heirs.

565
00:51:03.227 --> 00:51:06.438
from this time forward.
with our gratitude.

566
00:51:06.439 --> 00:51:07.481
I will.

567
00:51:07.482 --> 00:51:09.024
Please note the mine field

568
00:51:09.025 --> 00:51:11.610
